Package org.ldaptive.schema

Interface Summary
SchemaElement Interface for schema elements.
 

Class Summary
AbstractNamedSchemaElement Base schema bean for named schema elements.
AbstractSchemaElement Base class for schema elements.
AttributeType Bean for an attribute type schema element.
DITContentRule Bean for a DIT content rule schema element.
DITStructureRule Bean for a DIT content rule schema element.
Extensions Bean for an extension found in a schema element.
MatchingRule Bean for an matching rule schema element.
MatchingRuleUse Bean for an matching rule use schema element.
NameForm Bean for a name form schema element.
ObjectClass Bean for an object class schema element.
Schema Bean that contains the schema definitions in RFC 4512.
SchemaFactory Factory to create Schema objects from an LDAP entry.
SchemaUtils Provides utility methods for this package.
Syntax Bean for an attribute syntax schema element.
 

Enum Summary
AttributeUsage Enum for an attribute usage schema element.
ObjectClassType Enum for an attribute usage schema element.
